<section id="pool" class="section-padding bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0" data-aos="fade-right">
        <div class="position-relative">
          <img 
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/261102/pexels-photo-261102.jpeg" 
            alt="Infinity Pool" 
            class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg"
          >
          <div class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 bg-primary text-white p-3 rounded-bottom-start">
            <i class="fas fa-water me-2"></i> Infinity Edge
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-4">
          <div class="col-6">
            <img 
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/221457/pexels-photo-221457.jpeg" 
              alt="Pool Loungers" 
              class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
            >
          </div>
          <div class="col-6">
            <img 
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3225531/pexels-photo-3225531.jpeg" 
              alt="Pool Bar" 
              class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-left">
        <h2 class="section-title">Luxurious Swimming Pools</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-4">Dive into relaxation with our stunning pool facilities</p>
        <p>Our resort features two magnificent swimming pools designed to provide the ultimate relaxation experience. The infinity edge pool seems to merge with the horizon of the Arabian Sea, creating a breathtaking visual spectacle that has become the signature feature of our property.</p>
        <p>The family-friendly pool area offers shallow sections for children and comfortable loungers for parents to relax while keeping an eye on their little ones. Both pools are surrounded by lush tropical gardens, providing a serene environment for swimming and sunbathing.</p>
        
        <div class="pool-details mt-4">
          <h4>Pool Features</h4>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Temperature-controlled water</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Infinity edge design</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Dedicated children's area</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Underwater lighting</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Poolside service</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Swim-up bar</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Premium loungers & cabanas</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Towel service</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pool-hours mt-4">
          <h4>Hours & Guidelines</h4>
          <p><i class="far fa-clock text-primary me-2"></i> <strong>Operating Hours:</strong> 7:00 AM - 8:00 PM</p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i> <strong>Safety Guidelines:</strong></p>
          <ul class="small">
            <li>Children under 12 must be accompanied by an adult</li>
            <li>No diving in shallow areas</li>
            <li>Shower before entering the pool</li>
            <li>No glassware around the pool area</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>